Introduction
Burp Suite is one of the most widely used tools for Web Application Penetration Testing.

It acts as an intercepting proxy, allowing you to view, modify, and replay HTTP/HTTPS traffic between your browser and a web server.

Almost every professional penetration tester uses Burp Suite during web security assessments.

Why Burp Suite?
Normally, when you visit a website:

