Main Components
1. Proxy ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
Purpose:

Intercept requests before they reach the server.

Functions:

Capture Requests
Modify Requests
Drop Requests
Forward Requests
2. HTTP History (Logger)
Records every request and response.

Example:

GET /login

POST /login

GET /dashboard

GET /profile
Useful for reviewing previous traffic.

3. Repeater ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐
Allows sending the same request repeatedly after making changes.

Example:

Original:

GET /profile?id=5
Modified:

GET /profile?id=6
Perfect for manual testing.

4. Intruder
Automates sending many requests.

Used for:

Brute Force
Fuzzing
Parameter Testing
Example payloads:

admin

administrator

root

guest
5. Decoder
Used for encoding and decoding data.

Supports:

Base64
URL Encoding
HTML Encoding
Hex
Example:

c29oYW0=
↓

soham
6. Comparer
Compares two requests or responses.

Useful for identifying small differences.

7. Target
Shows the structure of a web application.

Example:

/

/login

/profile

/admin

/api

/settings
